If you shoot it,

553
00:31:25,240 --> 00:31:26,640
then it means my skill is not god enough.

554
00:31:27,040 --> 00:31:28,920
Your Highness, you are really broad-minded.

555
00:31:29,560 --> 00:31:32,040
Have you harvested much?

556
00:31:39,560 --> 00:31:40,560
It's still empty.

557
00:31:42,120 --> 00:31:44,760
Father did change the hunting rule this year.

558
00:31:45,440 --> 00:31:46,560
Judging by the number of preys of birds,

559
00:31:47,560 --> 00:31:49,480
it's more difficult than previous years.

560
00:31:51,160 --> 00:31:54,600
No wonder you just hunted a pheasant.

561
00:31:55,280 --> 00:31:56,800
You changed the horse on the field,

562
00:31:57,680 --> 00:31:59,320
which will certainly affect your performance.

563
00:31:59,960 --> 00:32:02,080
I can't blame the horse for my poor shooting skills.

564
00:32:02,440 --> 00:32:03,040
I

565
00:32:03,320 --> 00:32:05,200
hunted three crows, two sparrows

566
00:32:05,440 --> 00:32:06,520
and a lark.

567
00:32:07,080 --> 00:32:07,880
What about this?

568
00:32:09,440 --> 00:32:10,560
I will give you one of my preys.

569
00:32:11,320 --> 00:32:12,840
You can regard it as yours.

570
00:32:13,360 --> 00:32:14,600
Neither of us tell it to others.

571
00:32:15,280 --> 00:32:16,720
Father won't know it, either.

572
00:32:17,320 --> 00:32:18,200
Thank you for your kindness, brother.

573
00:32:19,040 --> 00:32:20,320
I don't have good shooting skills,.

574
00:32:20,840 --> 00:32:22,600
let alone resort to trickery

575
00:32:22,880 --> 00:32:24,080
to cheat father.

576
00:32:26,400 --> 00:32:27,160
You're really ambitious!

577
00:32:28,520 --> 00:32:29,960
Good luck to you!

578
00:32:30,720 --> 00:32:32,560
You'd better hurry up.

579
00:32:33,360 --> 00:32:34,960
Six hours

580
00:32:36,120 --> 00:32:37,520
will be up soon.

581
00:33:39,720 --> 00:33:40,280
Catch it.

582
00:33:41,320 --> 00:33:43,360
It was shot by you.

583
00:33:43,800 --> 00:33:45,160
If you didn't shoot,

584
00:33:45,560 --> 00:33:47,200
maybe it's I who am lying on the ground now.

585
00:33:47,720 --> 00:33:48,960
You deserve to have the golden eagle.

586
00:33:50,040 --> 00:33:51,080
I am Ye Qingti.

587
00:33:51,440 --> 00:33:52,840
Thank you for saving me.

588
00:33:53,120 --> 00:33:54,160
Ye Qingti?

589
00:33:55,760 --> 00:33:57,240
Are you from the family of Duke Yongning?

590
00:33:57,720 --> 00:33:59,440
My father is Duke Yongning, Ye Zhenguan.

591
00:33:59,760 --> 00:34:01,360
What's your name, please?

592
00:34:02,240 --> 00:34:03,040
Song Xuanren.

593
00:34:03,960 --> 00:34:04,840
Crown Prince.

594
00:34:05,720 --> 00:34:06,560
I'm sorry to be impolite.

595
00:34:07,000 --> 00:34:07,760
Forget it.

596
00:34:08,520 --> 00:34:10,280
I've heard that you guard the frontier

597
00:34:10,520 --> 00:34:11,360
with eminent achievements.

598
00:34:11,880 --> 00:34:13,840
I regret not to have known you before.

599
00:34:14,200 --> 00:34:16,440
It's my honor to hunt with you.

600
00:34:17,150 --> 00:34:18,560
The golden eagle was hunted by you.

601
00:34:19,440 --> 00:34:20,280
It's not mine.

602
00:34:21,600 --> 00:34:22,840
Your Highness, you shot the pheasant first

603
00:34:23,150 --> 00:34:25,040
and then used it to attract the golden eagle.

604
00:34:25,360 --> 00:34:26,710
You behave carefully at each step with supreme wisdom.

605
00:34:26,960 --> 00:34:27,760
I really appreciate you.

606
00:34:28,280 --> 00:34:30,600
Naturally the prey belongs to you.

607
00:34:31,710 --> 00:34:32,920
I'm leaving.

608
00:34:50,280 --> 00:34:51,360
Where is Crown Prince?

609
00:34:52,600 --> 00:34:56,800
The Crown Prince hasn't been back yet.

610
00:35:00,320 --> 00:35:01,080
Father,

611
00:35:02,120 --> 00:35:03,840
I just saw His Highness.

612
00:35:04,120 --> 00:35:05,840
Without many preys,

613
00:35:06,160 --> 00:35:07,360
I think maybe he is still looking for preys.

614
00:35:07,680 --> 00:35:09,360
So the time was delayed.

615
00:35:10,880 --> 00:35:12,680
Worthless!

616
00:35:18,000 --> 00:35:18,960
Chief Eunuch!

617
00:35:25,200 --> 00:35:25,920
By the way,

618
00:35:26,480 --> 00:35:29,080
have you finished counting the preys of

619
00:35:29,280 --> 00:35:30,880
the princes and sons of the aristocratic families?

620
00:35:31,480 --> 00:35:32,400
Your Majesty,

621
00:35:32,680 --> 00:35:34,080
it's almost done.

622
00:35:34,320 --> 00:35:35,800
Among all the princes,

623
00:35:36,080 --> 00:35:39,160
the Eldest Prince hunted the most.

624
00:35:39,400 --> 00:35:41,000
Among all the sons of the aristocratic families,

625
00:35:41,280 --> 00:35:42,880
it's...

626
00:35:47,640 --> 00:35:48,080
He is back.

627
00:35:48,200 --> 00:35:49,160
His Highness is back.

628
00:35:50,720 --> 00:35:54,120
Your Majesty, His Highness is back.

629
00:36:00,600 --> 00:36:02,760
I'm sorry I'm late. Please forgive me, father.

630
00:36:02,960 --> 00:36:04,040
Where is your prey?

631
00:36:10,280 --> 00:36:11,080
A golden eagle!

632
00:36:13,320 --> 00:36:14,440
He deserves to be the Crown Prince.

633
00:36:20,080 --> 00:36:20,720
Good.

634
00:36:20,920 --> 00:36:21,640
Xuanren.

635
00:36:22,760 --> 00:36:25,000
Unexpectedly, you hunted a golden eagle.

636
00:36:25,320 --> 00:36:27,320
It's hard to get it.

637
00:36:33,040 --> 00:36:35,960
As for the hunting in the paddock,

638
00:36:36,440 --> 00:36:37,840
according to the rules,

639
00:36:38,840 --> 00:36:42,280
with hunting a golden eagle,

640
00:36:42,520 --> 00:36:44,200
His Highness got the first place.

641
00:36:44,520 --> 00:36:47,640
He is awarded a ferghana horse,

642
00:36:47,840 --> 00:36:50,200
a Mubai Sword,

643
00:36:50,440 --> 00:36:53,120
a plain silver armor with gold wire.

644
00:36:54,040 --> 00:36:58,800
The Eldest Prince and General Ye also performed well.

645
00:36:59,800 --> 00:37:03,040
They are awarded a ferghana horse each.

646
00:37:03,840 --> 00:37:09,040
As for other people, go to get your awards by yourself.

647
00:37:09,280 --> 00:37:11,360
- Thank you, Your Majesty. - Thank you, father.

648
00:37:17,160 --> 00:37:18,040
Your Majesty, you are not in good health.

649
00:37:18,280 --> 00:37:19,880
It's good to return to the palace early.

650
00:37:20,920 --> 00:37:21,960
One more thing.

651
00:37:23,400 --> 00:37:25,920
I received a battlefield report,

652
00:37:26,840 --> 00:37:28,280
saying the State of Chong'an

653
00:37:28,720 --> 00:37:30,600
frequently disturbed our border recently.

654
00:37:31,640 --> 00:37:36,720
So the first prize winner of the hunting today

655
00:37:37,000 --> 00:37:40,960
should go on an expedition instead of me
to pacify the disturbance in the border

656
00:37:41,600 --> 00:37:45,720
and show the national prestige of our State of Chengyu.

657
00:37:46,280 --> 00:37:47,240
As you wish.

658
00:37:48,520 --> 00:37:49,880
I'm sure to succeed in carrying out the assignment.

659
00:37:50,880 --> 00:37:51,800
Xuanren.

660
00:37:53,320 --> 00:37:56,640
I appoint you as the commander in chief of the troops,

661
00:37:57,360 --> 00:37:59,000
can you pacify the disturbance?

662
00:37:59,360 --> 00:38:00,000
Your Majesty.

663
00:38:01,160 --> 00:38:02,440
Although the State of Chong'an is a big state,

664
00:38:03,000 --> 00:38:05,440
our State of Chengyu is administered
by father with kindness.

665
00:38:05,760 --> 00:38:06,560
Working together as a whole country

666
00:38:06,960 --> 00:38:08,520
and protected by the Lingbi Stone,

667
00:38:08,800 --> 00:38:09,680
it's destined

668
00:38:10,400 --> 00:38:12,320
to beat the enemies.

669
00:38:12,760 --> 00:38:15,840
Good. You deserve to be the Crown Prince.

670
00:38:16,480 --> 00:38:19,200
It's my duty to share your worries and burdens.

671
00:38:21,760 --> 00:38:22,560
Ren,

672
00:38:23,000 --> 00:38:24,560
it's the first time for you to go an expedition.

673
00:38:25,320 --> 00:38:29,080
I have chosen a general

674
00:38:29,400 --> 00:38:31,040
to help you.

675
00:38:31,480 --> 00:38:33,880
I'm wondering who you chose.

676
00:38:34,200 --> 00:38:37,640
The son of Duke Yongning, Ye Qingti.

677
00:38:44,880 --> 00:38:46,960
Pay my visit to you, Your Majesty,

678
00:38:47,840 --> 00:38:48,720
Your Highness.

679
00:38:49,800 --> 00:38:50,760
Forget it.

680
00:38:53,600 --> 00:38:56,120
Xuanren, Duke Yongning

681
00:38:56,920 --> 00:38:59,920
spread their martial arts from generation to generation.
They're brave and skillful in battle.

682
00:39:00,440 --> 00:39:04,280
All the generations go to fight in the battlefield
and repay the country with supreme loyalty.

683
00:39:04,880 --> 00:39:07,720
Among the younger generation,

684
00:39:08,040 --> 00:39:09,520
Ye Qingti is the most outstanding one.

685
00:39:10,280 --> 00:39:13,160
I have appointed him as your vice commander.

686
00:39:14,480 --> 00:39:16,760
I'm sure to help His Highness in my full support.

687
00:39:17,560 --> 00:39:18,440
Father, you really considered thoroughly.

688
00:39:18,880 --> 00:39:20,760
I will lead the army to the battlefield tomorrow.

689
00:39:21,080 --> 00:39:21,880
Good.

690
00:39:33,560 --> 00:39:35,040
Si Ming, finally you're back.

691
00:39:39,400 --> 00:39:40,640
Si Ming.

692
00:39:59,240 --> 00:40:00,080
Your Highness.

693
00:40:03,080 --> 00:40:03,720
Turn up.

694
00:40:08,320 --> 00:40:10,600
You read His Majesty's Book of Fate secretly!

695
00:40:11,160 --> 00:40:13,920
Only you can do such a thing.

696
00:40:14,120 --> 00:40:15,160
How dare you not admit after doing it?

697
00:40:15,320 --> 00:40:17,560
It's not what you always do.

698
00:40:31,520 --> 00:40:33,000
I just come to play with you.

699
00:40:33,440 --> 00:40:34,720
Why are you so nervous?

700
00:40:36,400 --> 00:40:37,360
What did you see?

701
00:40:37,760 --> 00:40:38,880
What are you saying?

702
00:40:39,720 --> 00:40:40,960
His Majesty's Book of Fate.

703
00:40:41,840 --> 00:40:42,400
No.

704
00:40:42,760 --> 00:40:43,640
Tell me the truth.

705
00:40:46,000 --> 00:40:47,520
Is it true in the Book of Fate?

706
00:40:48,160 --> 00:40:50,080
It says the state where His Majesty
is experiencing his misfortunes

707
00:40:50,120 --> 00:40:51,280
is having a battlement with the neighboring state.

708
00:40:51,640 --> 00:40:52,760
It's a dangerous battle that His Majesty

709
00:40:52,760 --> 00:40:54,040
has to go to have an expedition by himself.

710
00:40:54,960 --> 00:40:56,840
So you plan to go to the mortal realm secretly

711
00:40:57,120 --> 00:40:58,760
to see His Majesty.

712
00:41:00,160 --> 00:41:01,640
You said if I went to the mortal realm,

713
00:41:01,880 --> 00:41:03,320
it would affect His Majesty's experiencing his misfortunes.

714
00:41:03,480 --> 00:41:04,760
So I won't go there.

715
00:41:05,200 --> 00:41:06,360
Even if I went to the mortal realm,

716
00:41:06,680 --> 00:41:08,400
I would just glance at him secretly.

717
00:41:08,680 --> 00:41:09,440
Can I do that?

718
00:41:09,680 --> 00:41:11,040
No way.

719
00:41:11,560 --> 00:41:12,920
I just cast a glance at him.

720
00:41:13,120 --> 00:41:14,960
I won't disturb His Majesty.

721
00:41:15,600 --> 00:41:16,400
Can I do that?

722
00:41:16,600 --> 00:41:18,600
What if His Majesty was just in danger

723
00:41:18,840 --> 00:41:20,560
when you glanced at him secretly?

724
00:41:20,920 --> 00:41:22,920
Can you stand by doing nothing?

725
00:41:24,480 --> 00:41:25,000
I...

726
00:41:25,000 --> 00:41:26,200
Of course you can't.

727
00:41:26,720 --> 00:41:28,720
It's certain that you will help him.

728
00:41:29,000 --> 00:41:29,680
But Your Highness,

729
00:41:29,920 --> 00:41:31,840
if fairies use magic arts in the mortal realm,

730
00:41:32,080 --> 00:41:33,000
they must be backfired.

731
00:41:33,280 --> 00:41:34,200
As for the result of the backfire,

732
00:41:34,400 --> 00:41:36,720
you can't stand it.

733
00:41:38,200 --> 00:41:39,600
How serious is it?

734
00:41:40,680 --> 00:41:42,040
You will be backfired

735
00:41:42,320 --> 00:41:44,720
by the same degree of your magic arts.

736
00:41:45,720 --> 00:41:48,040
Not only your fairy power will be destroyed badly,

737
00:41:48,560 --> 00:41:50,560
but also it may harm your immortal root.

738
00:41:51,200 --> 00:41:53,160
It's difficult to recover.

739
00:41:58,560 --> 00:41:59,320
So serious?

740
00:41:59,720 --> 00:42:03,040
Your Highness, give up the idea.

741
00:42:05,160 --> 00:42:06,160
Since you said I couldn't go there,

742
00:42:06,440 --> 00:42:07,520
then I won't go.

743
00:42:07,960 --> 00:42:08,600
Don't worry.

744
00:42:08,960 --> 00:42:10,280
Just be busy with your things. I'm leaving.

745
00:42:10,320 --> 00:42:10,640
OK.

746
00:42:28,720 --> 00:42:30,360
Si Ming said if I went there,

747
00:42:31,360 --> 00:42:32,880
it would affect His Majesty's experiencing his misfortunes.

748
00:42:34,160 --> 00:42:36,280
However, to experience his misfortunes

749
00:42:37,120 --> 00:42:39,080
means he must be in danger.

750
00:42:40,040 --> 00:42:41,200
Si Ming also said

751
00:42:42,200 --> 00:42:43,360
if I used magic arts in the mortal realm,

752
00:42:43,680 --> 00:42:45,080
I would be certainly backfired.

753
00:42:45,640 --> 00:42:47,200
What can I do?

754
00:42:50,160 --> 00:42:51,040
If I want to repay his kindness,

755
00:42:51,600 --> 00:42:53,360
I can't just think of myself.

756
00:42:54,600 --> 00:42:57,760
Anyway, I must go to have a look.

